values.value: OUR RECORDS INDICATE THAT THE PREMIUM WAS NOT RECEIVED FOR THE WEEK IN WHICH THE SERVICE WAS PERFORMED. TO ENSURE THAT YOUR CLAIM CAN BE PROCESSED, PLEASE SUBMIT YOUR PREMIUM PAYMENT WITHIN THE GRACE PERIOD AS DESCRIBED IN YOUR POLICY. IF PREMIUM IS RECEIVED WITHIN THE GRACE PERIOD, THE CLAIM WILL BE PROCESSED ACCORDING TO THE TERMS OF YOUR POLICY. IF PREMIUM HAS BEEN PAID SINCE THE DATE OF THIS NOTICE, PLEASE DISREGARD.
